<br>
I went to Mistmoore, but gods it gets boring after a while.  Anything quicker?  Preferably something I can do solo. <p><center><img src="http://www.sparnak.com/~sparnak/sig1.jpg"></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ubandose.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bandose</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 65<br> <font color=#333333>(5/17/02 12:56:03 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=379.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Ring of Scale Faction</span><hr size=1> I loaded the point-blank AE's and helped farm in MM for most of a day.  I'm still KOS to RoS as well.  I'd also appreciate tips here. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/utrezark.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Trezark</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master Summoner</span><br>  Posts: 151<br> <font color=#333333>(5/17/02 10:10:50 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=379.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://shadowblazer.armageddongames.com/images/Trezark/ezhmage.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Ring of Scale Faction</span><hr size=1> Keel some bards.  I camped Vhalen Nostrolo back in my 20's or 30's for about one level, and was pleasently surprised the first time I conned Gorenaire and found that I was kindly.  I think even after spending several hours in SF trying to get spell drops, I'm <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> still</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> either kindly or amiably to Gore (haven't had the guts to go look for her since my most recent wurm slaughterfest).<br>
<br>
Of course if you're not a Dark Elf, this might not be a viable tactic for you <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><BR><CENTER><hr size=1 WIDTH=75%>
